#准备工作

1. VPSx1
2. 域名x1
3. cloudflare账号x1

#开始

##域名添加到cloudflare

1. DNS填好之后记得把Proxy status打开，云朵变成橙黄色显示Proxied。
2. SSL/TLS里面选择Flexible，然后在Edge Certificates里把TLS 1.3关闭。

##设置VPS时间

用`date -R` 查看当前时间，和PC时间不同的话改一下。

我用的Ubuntu 18.04，步骤如下：

1. 运行`tzselect`，按照提示选择区域

2. 复制文件

   ```bash
   cp /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai  /etc/localtime
   ```

3. 再用`date -R`查看应该就一致了。



##安装v2ray并配置

先更新一下系统

```bash
apt-get update
```

安装v2ray需要的unzip和daemon

```bash
apt install unzip daemon
```

安装v2ray

```
bash <(curl -L -s https://install.direct/go.sh)
```

修改配置文件

```bash
vim /etc/v2ray/config.json
```

配置文件示例：

```json
{
  "log": {
    "loglevel": "warning",
    "access": "/dev/null",
    "error": "/dev/null"
  },
  "inbounds": [{
    "listen":"127.0.0.1",
    "port": 10000, #端口号随意
    "protocol": "vmess",
    "settings": {
      "clients": [
        {
          "id": "de20d937-ca8f-af14-ea07-20b45447d371", #UUID改成自己的
          "level": 1,
          "alterId": 64
        }
      ]
    },
	"streamSettings": {
        "network": "ws",
        "wsSettings": {
        "path": "/bannedbook" #这里/后的设定也随意
        }
    }
  }],
  "outbounds": [
    {
      "protocol": "freedom",
      "settings": {},
      "tag": "allowed"
    },
    {
      "protocol": "blackhole",
      "settings": {},
      "tag": "blocked"
    }
  ],
  "routing": {
    "rules": [
      {
        "type": "field",
        "ip": [
          "geoip:private"
        ],
        "outboundTag": "blocked"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

配置后测试

```bash
/usr/bin/v2ray/v2ray -test -config /etc/v2ray/config.json
```



##安装nginx并配置

安装nginx

```bash
apt-get -y install nginx
```

然后替换/etc/nginx.conf为如下配置，此配置文件是通用配置，不管什么域名都可以使用，直接下载覆盖即可:

```bash
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bannedbook/fanqiang/master/v2ss/server-cfg/nginx.conf -O -> /etc/nginx/nginx.conf
```

之后修改一下nginx.conf，需要修改两处：

```
user www-data;
worker_processes auto;
pid /run/nginx.pid;
include /etc/nginx/modules-enabled/*.conf;
worker_rlimit_nofile  655350;
events {
	use epoll;
	worker_connections 65536;
}

http {
	sendfile on;
	tcp_nopush on;
	tcp_nodelay on;
	keepalive_timeout 65;
	types_hash_max_size 2048;
	include /etc/nginx/mime.types;
	default_type application/octet-stream;
	ssl_protocols TLSv1 TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2; # Dropping SSLv3, ref: POODLE
	ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;
	access_log /var/log/nginx-access.log;
	error_log /var/log/nginx-error.log;

	gzip on;
	server {
		listen 80 default_server;
		listen [::]:80 default_server;
		root /var/www/html;

		index index.html index.htm index.nginx-debian.html;

		server_name _;

		location / {
			try_files $uri $uri/ =404;
		}

    location /bannedbook { #与 V2Ray 配置中的 path 保持一致
	    proxy_redirect off;
	    proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:10000; #端口号同样
	    proxy_http_version 1.1;
	    proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
	    proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";
	    proxy_set_header Host $http_host;

	    # Show realip in v2ray access.log
	    proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
	    proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;	
    }	
	}
}
```

测试nginx配置`nginx -t`

重新载入配置`nginx -s reload`

在这里重启一下v2ray `service v2ray restart`



##客户端说明

###windows

用的v2rayN，和基本v2ray填写差不多。

地址填域名，端口443。

UUID和额外ID按照配置填写。

传输协议选WS。

路径填配置里的path，不要忘记/

底层传输安全选tls

###Andriod

客户端的话V2rayNG和BifrostV都可以用，配置和Windows差不多。

###iOS

客户端用shadowroket。其他相同照着填就ok。

[vue-awesome-swiper:GitHub](https://github.com/surmon-china/vue-awesome-swiper)

github里还有demo，可以参考。

轮播图+鼠标悬停就停止播放

1. 引入

`
npm install vue-awesome-swiper --save
`

全局引入：

```
import VueAwesomeSwiper from 'vue-awesome-swiper'
Vue.use(VueAwesomeSwiper)
import 'swiper/dist/css/swiper.css
```

在组件里引入
```
import 'swiper/dist/css/swiper.css'    //在全局没引入，这里记得要！
import { swiper, swiperSlide } from 'vue-awesome-swiper'

export default {
  components: {
    swiper,
    swiperSlide
  }
}
```

配置：
```html
<swiper :options="swiperOption" ref="mySwiper">
    <swiper-slide>I'm Slide 1</swiper-slide>
    <swiper-slide>I'm Slide 2</swiper-slide>
    <swiper-slide>I'm Slide 3</swiper-slide>
    <div class="swiper-pagination"  slot="pagination"></div>
  </swiper>
  ```
  ```js
  export default {
    name: 'carrousel',
    data() {
      return {
        swiperOption: {
            //自动播放
          autoplay: {
            delay: 4000,
            disableOnInteraction: false
          },
          slidesPerView: 3,
          spaceBetween: 30,
          pagination: {
            el: '.swiper-pagination',
            clickable: true
          }
        }
      }
    },
    computed: {
      swiper() {
        return this.$refs.mySwiper.swiper
      }
    },
    methods:{
        //鼠标悬停就停止播放，移开重新开始
        //需要加入 @mouseenter="on_top_enter“和@mouseleave="on_top_leave"
      on_top_enter(){
          this.swiper.autoplay.stop();
      },
      on_top_leave(){
          this.swiper.autoplay.start();
      }
    },
    mounted() {
      console.log('this is current swiper instance object', this.swiper)
      this.swiper.slideTo(3, 1000, false)
    }
  }
  ```

参考[v2ray白话文教程](https://toutyrater.github.io/basic/vmess.html)

1. 校准VPS时间
    ```bash
    //显示当前时间
    $ date -R

    //修改时间
    $ date --set="2020-03-19 13:17"
    ```

2. 下载脚本
    ```bash
    $ wget https://install.direct/go.sh
    ```
3. 安装脚本
    ```bash
    $ bash go.sh
    ```
4. 修改配置</br>
 - 获取UUID：[UUID自动生成](https://www.uuidgenerator.net/)
    ```bash
    $ vim /etc/v2ray/config.json
    ```
 - 设置putty中vim的右键粘贴：
    ```
    :set paste
    :set mouse=v
    ```

 - 配置格式
    ```json
    {
        "inbounds": [
            {
                "port": 16823, // 服务器监听端口
                "protocol": "vmess",    // 主传入协议
                "settings": {
                    "clients": [
                        {
                            "id": "b831381d-6324-4d53-ad4f-8cda48b30811",  // 用户 ID，客户端与服务器必须相同
                            "alterId": 64
                        }
                    ]
                }
            }
        ],
        "outbounds": [
            {
                "protocol": "freedom",  // 主传出协议
                "settings": {}
            }
        ]
    }
    ```
- 使用websocket的话：
    ```json
    {
        "inbounds": [
            {
                "port": 16823,
                "protocol": "vmess",
                "settings": {
                    "clients": [
                    {
                        "id": "4fddbfe5-9373-4d43-9d83-d8f1b9b2196f",
                        "alterId": 64
                    }
                ]
            },
            "streamSettings": {
                "wsSettings":{
          		 "path":"/",
         		 "headers":{}
        		},
                "network":"ws"
            }
        }
    ],
    "outbounds": [
            {
                "protocol": "freedom",
                "settings": {}
            }
        ]
    }
    ```
- 检测配置文件有没有错误，正确的是
    ```bash
    $ /usr/bin/v2ray/v2ray -test -config /etc/v2ray/config.json
    V2Ray v3.15 (die Commanderin) 20180329
    An unified platform for anti-censorship.
    Configuration OK.
    ```
5. 开启v2ray
    ```bash
    $ systemctl start v2ray
    ```
6. 开启BBR
    ```bash
    echo "net.core.default_qdisc=fq" >> /etc/sysctl.conf
    echo "net.ipv4.tcp_congestion_control=bbr" >> /etc/sysctl.conf
    sysctl -p
    ```
    - 测试一下
    ```bash
    $ lsmod | grep bbr
    tcp_bbr                20480  0
    ```
7. 完成。可能需要重启服务器之后才能

